caption.text: It has been 20 years since the last time I was this cute. Brows on fleek from birth baby try and top that.

Muchas gracias to the loveliest of my fellow Affan Miles aficionados for coming to see Paragita's performance yesterday (and me!). I hope we gave you a performance to remember, and lain kali ajakin yang lainnya yaaa hehehe. You guys and the other Affan Milers not present in the picture have been one of the biggest reasons for me to be able to survive college life and I'm more than glad I can share this special event and (more upcoming) with you all. :)
.
And as for you kelompencapir leuwiliang jero yang ngacangin gue tiap kali gue promosi di grup to surprise me, well, congratulations. You did. To see you berbondong sekampung datang jauh dari Bogor udik kalian masing-masing ke Kuningan bawa-bawa bunga di kereta as if mau lamaran dan bawa coklat di botol miras juga was beyond my expectations. I miss you too haha, and I miss kalian juga para perantau dan orang terasing (@krsnaretha, @kelvinmanalu, @liefarel, @cintyahapsari_, @albertuskristanto, among others). Lekas pulang yaa kami menanti oleh-oleh. Also, those letters are really touching and don't worry, my family won't read it. Per your request. Jadi inget dulu sempat tertegun the first time I saw kalian nyanyiin Mande-Mande dan jadi baper lagi waktu kita nyanyiin waktu pamit pulang. You know, it's kinda awkward because senior-senior gue pada tahu semua lagu itu hahahaa. Bottomline is I want to thank you all @vivarecisswara for your efforts, for they remind me that Paragita is not my only home, and I still have a family in you guys hehehe :')
.
Needless to say that the cellphone issue delayed this post and the vibe might have gone down a bit, but I just want to say that after all I've been through as soon as I got off that stage, and for those moments long before, I can't thank you enough.

#SemarakKarsa #PuspaIndonesia

caption.text:
Teruntuk @graciavarani
@keziaemanuella @jennifersurjono @cristiedina @marychristyhs @trifenaap @angelicashania @aminoar @kyrvs @naomipas @reginacinda @thannizafaurie @triratnaj @zoyanandina @almadeg @laurentiaa_ @sasqiaap @ivanakalit @hannatheresiaolivia @deddykim @_invrichard @fachryal_h @harry.ks @ridhoperka, dan beberapa yang akun Instagramnya belum gue temukan,
Anggota PSM UI Paragita
Angkatan 2016
‚Ä¢
‚Ä¢
Selamat dan selamat datang.
‚Ä¢
Pertama-tama I would like to thank you all sudah mengingatkan gue akan kebahagiaan menyaksikan lahiran adik-adik gue yang terakhir gue alami 14 dan 10 tahun yang lalu.
I mean, look at those faces, yang basah, yang merah, yang timing posenya kurang tepat, yang cuma nyempil setengah gak jelas, tapi bahagia.
‚Ä¢
It has just been four months but you have been through a lot of things together, and I can guarantee you that there is a lot more to come. Things that are even larger and heavier. Jalan di depan sana akan menanjak, berliku, dan pastinya tidak akan mulus. However, if you hold on together, kalian akan baik-baik saja and I am 100% sure of that, karena kini, kalian adalah rumah bagi satu sama lain; atap yang rela disorot terik dan diguyur hujan, dinding yang menjaga seisi rumah utuh dan tegak, lantai dan fondasi yang memberi dasar kokoh tahan guncangan, jendela yang memberi angin segar dan pemandangan, serta pintu yang selalu terbuka, selalu menyambut satu sama lain dengan tangan terbuka.
‚Ä¢
Please do make yourselves at home here. Kalian memang asalnya berbeda, kalian punya petualangan masing-masing dengan masalah-masalah yang berbeda pula. Namun camkan bahwa kemanapun kalian pergi, kalian bisa pulang kesini. Apapun kegundahan kalian, ketidaknyamanan kalian, kalian bisa ceritakan disini. Kita bisa cari solusinya bersama. Paragita bukan cuma nyanyi bareng doang. We're a family, and for a family, to lose one is to lose too much.
‚Ä¢
With all that said gue cuma mau bilang selamat berParagita, and don't forget to have fun and love in everything you do here.
‚Ä¢
Paragita menanti petualangan kita bersama.
‚Ä¢
‚Ä¢
Tertanda,
Yang tidurnya masih ngutang
#GabungParagita

‚Ä¢
